          <div class="section-heading">
            <h2>Classes</h2>
            
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
            <img src="nimg/strawberries.JPG" class="img-responsive" height="75%" width="75%">
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-8 col-md-8 text-left">
            <h4 class="">Food For Fertility</h4>
            <p>Before participating in classes, Judy first meets with patients 
              for a 60-minute <i>virtual</i> consultation. She works with patients to build 
              an individually-designed
              nutrition and fitness program based on their current lifestyle, labs, weight 
              and fertility plan in conjunction with their  health care provider.</p>
            <p>Food for Fertility’s highly interactive sessions offer participants lifestyle 
              counseling in a supportive group setting. The classes foster skills that enable 
              weight loss and fertility, focusing on healthy eating, meal-planning strategies, 
              and exercise habits. We cook, taste, meal plan, and partake in light exercise. 
              Our classes are now on a virtual platform. We cook together from our home kitchens.
              <!---After the class, we take an optional 30 minute walk along beautiful Lake Union.---> 
              The program consists of six weekly sessions on Saturday mornings; 
              each session is 90 minutes.</p>
